{"tid":701380,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泰妍 21歲細妹 😊","createTime":"2018-06-14T05:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T14:15:08.000Z","uid":44730,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1422e1e85ec5191ecf2ca34184d4b1b7681d72a1","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:46:28.000Z","msg":"阿哥就見過， 今次睇下細妹大左既真面目<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c28d050f35564b23509426b91e12fd7c/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-06-13/106404-623071.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c28d050f35564b23509426b91e12fd7c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-06-13%2F106404-623071.jpg&h=9eeab09b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8ec1869f64e9346d5af805bde8808867618082b","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/08NQOdLVNxY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F08NQOdLVNxY&d=6TJGeoF8cj8vgOXsNTft2NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c441ab6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/08NQOdLVNxY</a>"},{"pid":"c8a020be244797d0c29eb841dafb2ae58718a486","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wlEQ3ic_zdU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwlEQ3ic_zdU&d=6TJGeoF8cj8vgOXsNTft2NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c6d32ed1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wlEQ3ic_zdU</a><br />\n<br />\n翻唱一首Sabrina Carpenter《Why》，就足以讓人入坑~"},{"pid":"2cddf0c99b305578ca622ca4f30dd806c94bd468","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"泰妍一家神基因！親妹金夏妍網上翻唱《Why》正式曝光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/133803_d79817d59e9e6c5d8dd702ef75323129.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F133803_d79817d59e9e6c5d8dd702ef75323129.gif&h=e7dc9c52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98ac02f0b0e91e8196b3ff9c62765398513db014","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"少時泰妍哥哥曝光後，粉絲對一直未有正式露面的夏妍更感好奇，網上更流傳着很多據說是「泰妍親妹妹」的照片，但其實不少都是假的！而早在2015年也有消息指，夏妍成功透過SM娛樂的非公開選秀，正式開始練習生生涯，不少粉絲都期待是繼Jessica和Krystal後第二對「SM姐妹花」。而本月（11日）1998年出生，今年只有21歲（韓國年齡）的夏妍終於正式出現在大家眼前。夏妍發佈翻唱Sabrina Carpenter的《Why》影片，除了可愛的面容，更大展清新的唱功，不禁令人讚嘆「金家」孩子都擁有一把悅耳的嗓子。而帶少許嬰兒肥的夏妍，與姊姊泰妍在少時出道前輪廓也非常相似呢！"},{"pid":"2e5b32835ecadcf580f5fcdc11cdbc45d9f4631b","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:50:00.000Z","msg":"曾在SNAPCHAT公開過和妹妹金夏妍（音譯）的合照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ea86e7e9a48358023f66027711000aea/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-06-13/106404-623070.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ea86e7e9a48358023f66027711000aea%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-06-13%2F106404-623070.jpeg&h=3af96f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1ba76be80e781a2753d6b159eac4437a/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-06-13/106404-623077.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1ba76be80e781a2753d6b159eac4437a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-06-13%2F106404-623077.jpg&h=22325a40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d2e83a8508f97336031346fd4ba6f89d23313ea","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:52:50.000Z","msg":"睇佢可能會跟家姐入娛樂圈<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8186a68a9543d16ed1ba34bac2e2979f65945995","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:53:55.000Z","msg":"雖然夏妍正式出道的日期仍未確定，但SONE都非常期待她與姊姊的天籟合作，而泰妍亦準備在6月18日發行特別專輯《Something New》，作為送給SONE的禮物。可惜的是，是次夏日新曲將不會進行音樂節目宣傳和打歌，只是作為一份特別的禮物，送給一直等待着泰妍音樂的粉絲。另一方面，泰妍將會在6月15日展開日本見面會《TAEYEON - JAPAN SHOW CASE TOUR 2018-》，在福岡、東京和大阪等地，進行4場見面會和日本SONE見面。"},{"pid":"d7701e94d3c4abeeeb95590486f589b26ceef862","tid":701380,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"同一個醫生"},{"pid":"82a6132fc8f17ee286301ec6564df07f19cbc5d4","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2018-06-13/106404-623076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2018-06-13%2F106404-623076.jpg&h=647bb65b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n能看出來金夏妍是音樂志願生，標準流利的英語發音，配上清雅明亮的嗓音，雖然聲音辨識度不高，但聽著挺舒服的。"},{"pid":"0a483255326f052e242c681025f5c3a083641fd7","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"夏妍的外貌公開，少不免被網民拿來和姐姐比較！網民紛紛吐糟妹妹的樣貌不如泰妍般精緻，不過也有很多粉絲表示夏妍和泰妍的眼睛、鼻子也很相似，除了臉上的嬰兒肥之外，和10年前剛剛出道的泰妍長得也挺像啊～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HC9YZlh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHC9YZlh.jpg&h=75bccb21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5052a3f123c854407b7f2aa1bb5421cb2a86d4eb","tid":701380,"uid":70274,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a483255326f052e242c681025f5c3a083641fd7","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"夏妍的外貌公開，少不免被網民拿來和姐姐比較！網民紛紛吐糟妹妹的樣貌不如泰妍般精緻，不過也有很多粉絲表示夏妍和泰妍的眼睛、鼻子也很相似，除了臉上的嬰兒肥之外，和10年前剛剛出道的泰妍長得也挺像啊～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HC9YZlh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHC9YZlh.jpg&h=75bccb21&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"之後個樣一定會變既<br />\n佢地仲有幾次青春期同減肥瘦左"},{"pid":"1640f21f9e5c788c5ed46b594f7de4eef8bb79b8","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:14:12.000Z","msg":"▼這張年代更加久遠的兒時照片，也可以看出兩姐妹強大的基因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.bomb01.com/upload/news/original/74714254fcb8214b455b602800546eb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bomb01.com%2Fupload%2Fnews%2Foriginal%2F74714254fcb8214b455b602800546eb0.jpg&h=d6a31636&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3446dd5f514b2805deb89a19bb6f0b1248323f84","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"▼下面這一張就是在網路瘋傳的夏妍舊照，雖然化了妝讓她看起來有些成熟，不過五官輪廓確實和泰妍有些相似。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.bomb01.com/upload/news/original/838dce3434ccb7284399505e9492c466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bomb01.com%2Fupload%2Fnews%2Foriginal%2F838dce3434ccb7284399505e9492c466.jpg&h=8bdbfce2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4efbd37098b3b6a0e260c746b35270e30016d963","tid":701380,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"太肥喇佢"},{"pid":"b5bd8e7127486572c201a3d9056a53a74cefb0a9","tid":701380,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:29:35.000Z","msg":"外表路人到無得再路人"},{"pid":"11c6d82dbfd0af69d9dfd3bb57b43337dc4a58b7","tid":701380,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:33:15.000Z","msg":"咁快就21啦，時間過得真係快，泰妍為左佢個妹真係好辛苦，希望佢都努力同成功，不過通常有星光護航未必係好事，好多星二代都捱唔住外界俾嘅壓力，通常都好快半途而廢..."},{"pid":"6e703077ac0ebd15c9ccd7aee82b49d678515461","tid":701380,"uid":44638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"要執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f66778ae86798a0da97f86fd9f4ee461f9643fd","tid":701380,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"典型蒙古人樣"},{"pid":"9d09ff9f3aadb65895a29e04f48fb989548eac80","tid":701380,"uid":86727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"姐姐比她早出道也沒這嬰兒肥<br />\nIU是15歲出道才有一點點而已<br />\n<br />\n臉也太脹了吧⋯<br />\n21了⋯還嬰兒肥，那是真心肥吧"},{"pid":"cbf9893ace0787aefdff338953fe5ddea0b24422","tid":701380,"uid":63057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82a6132fc8f17ee286301ec6564df07f19cbc5d4","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2018-06-13/106404-623076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2018-06-13%2F106404-623076.jpg&h=647bb65b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n能看出來金夏妍是音樂志願生，標準流利的英語發音，配上清雅明亮的嗓音，雖然聲音辨識度不高，但聽著挺舒服的。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:30:17.000Z","msg":"個鼻....."},{"pid":"5b6f81ce330b4da34e9cf8fa22baccfa41f76493","tid":701380,"uid":106291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"要再整整 反正科技咁發達"},{"pid":"1dbc193df7c8130cb5089529a39f91f897af3225","tid":701380,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"叫SM既整容醫院幫佢執執囉...<br />\n個樣生成咁<br />\n唱到識飛都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9775ad2307c5e90c25b648b3c9644e7c49b70acc","tid":701380,"uid":70274,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"唔使擔心喎 <br />\nSm花叢黎 入到去一陣就會變靚<br />\n有錢唔理咩樣總之你有眼耳口鼻就得"},{"pid":"1ab7e6fb8b7fa3757eeb4372edea0633fa6d003b","tid":701380,"uid":815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3446dd5f514b2805deb89a19bb6f0b1248323f84","tid":701380,"uid":44730,"like":